* Overview
** Runlevels
+ Red Hat
0 - halt
1 - Single User (Rescue)
2 - multi-user (no-networking)
3 - multi-user (networking)
4 - Not used
5 - multi-user (Gui)
6 - restart

+ Debian
0 - halt
1 - Single User (Rescue)
2 - multi-user 
3 - Not used
4 - multi-user
5 - multi-user
6 - restart

